member.summary:
Class that holds the settings for the contour cut toolpath function.
Example usage:
var ts = new ToolpathSettings();
ts.Sorting=0;//Closest
// Set other properties...
ts.Save();

Keyboard class for handling key events
Example to check if a key is pressed:
Keyboard keyboard = new Keyboard();
keyboard.Install();
if(keyboard[Key.ESCAPE])
   DoSomething();
keyboard.Uninstall();
